# @custom-repo/infra-cache

Cache

## Installation

```bash
pnpm add @custom-repo/infra-cache
```

## Usage

```typescript
import { Cache } from '@custom-repo/infra-cache';
```

## Development

```bash
# Build
pnpm exec nx build infra-cache

# Test
pnpm exec nx test infra-cache

# Lint
pnpm exec nx lint infra-cache
```
